              "title": "教官的帽子"
            },
            "flower_of_life": {
              "desc": "教官的胸口别着这种花的时候，意味着今日不练兵。",
              "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/reliquary/Instructor/flower_of_life_icon.png",
              "position": "生之花",
              "title": "教官的胸花"
            },
            "goblet_of_eonothem": {
              "desc": "虽然在外人看来只是普通的茶杯，但在学员眼里可是教官权力的象征。",
              "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/reliquary/Instructor/goblet_of_eonothem_icon.png",
