              "desc": "熟知如何化解攻击力道的教官，不会让这种羽饰被劲风吹掉。",
              "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/reliquary/Instructor/plume_of_death_icon.png",
              "position": "死之羽",
              "title": "教官的羽饰"
            },
            "sands_of_eon": {
              "desc": "不能用来看时间的怀表，是完全奉献给训练的计时工具。",
              "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/reliquary/Instructor/sands_of_eon_icon.png",
